extends ../layouts/layout

block content
  h1 Tire Swap & Balance
  p.muted Seasonal changeovers, balancing, and quick puncture repairs.

  figure.service-hero
    img(src="/images/services/tires.jpg", alt="Tire Service hero image")

  h3 What’s included
  ul
    li Swap summer/winter sets (on rims or off rims)
    li Spin balance for smooth, vibration-free driving
    li Tire pressure check & TPMS reset (where applicable)
    li Puncture repair (plug/patch) available

  h3 Starting at $69
  p.muted Pricing varies by wheel size and whether tires are mounted on rims.

  p
    a.btn(href="/book") Book tire service